These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, train
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Transport   | train | skateboard | taxi |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: british, argentine, canadian
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the british is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality       | argentine | canadian | british |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, trike, bike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Transport         | bike     | trike | boat |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
3 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, horse
1. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the dog##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the horse##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Pet         | turtle  | dog | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, electrician, scientist
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the scientist is between the police-officer and the canadian##2
2. the electrician is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job         | police-officer   | scientist | electrician    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the canadian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the chinese##1
3. the chinese is in an odd position##4
4. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | canadian   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
3 different games are played: whist, domino, mah-jongg
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing whist is between the owner of the turtle and the person playing mah-jongg##2
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | whist | domino |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, car, helicopter
1. the person driving the train is between the person driving the car and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Transport    | car    | train | helicopter     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, ferret, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Pet   | lizard   | ferret  | snake  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

