.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, fuchsia, purple
There 3 different types of food: corn, garlic, pineapple
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Color   | ebony    | purple      | fuchsia |
| Food       | garlic | pineapple | corn   |

