.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, crime, adventure
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre         | crime | adventure | time-travel |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

