.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different games are played: poker, canasta, chess
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Game   | chess  | poker | canasta   |
