.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, writing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, zombie, romance
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person watching zombie movies##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | photography | writing | baking |
| Movie-Genre     | family    | romance  | zombie   |

