.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | water  | tea     | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

