.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry, ritmeester
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Cigar     | old-henry  | ritmeester   | blend |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 